* Iron snapped her head over her shoulder as she heard footsteps behind her, 
jumping towards the wall a second later and climbing to the roof as a set of 
charges hit the door and it burst open...a toxic ooze slithering out onto 
the floor.
She slipped into the little hole and made and journeyed quietly until she 
could see Necromancer and Hell Drak under her.*
